quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  6,101,Badī`u As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđi 'Anná Yakūnu Lahu Waladun Wa Lam Takun Lahu Şāĥibatun Wa Khalaqa Kulla Shay'in Wa Huwa Bikulli Shay'in `Alīmun
  6,102,Dhalikumu Allāhu Rabbukum Lā 'Ilāha 'Illā Huwa Khāliqu Kulli Shay'in Fā`budūhu Wa Huwa `Alá Kulli Shay'in Wa Kīlun
  6,103,Lā Tudrikuhu Al-'Abşāru Wa Huwa Yudriku Al-'Abşāra Wa Huwa Al-Laţīfu Al-Khabīr
  6,104,Qad Jā'akum Başā'iru Min Rabbikum Faman 'Abşara Falinafsihi Wa Man `Amiya Fa`alayhā Wa Mā 'Anā `Alaykum Biĥafīžin
  6,105,Wa Kadhalika Nuşarrifu Al-'Āyāti Wa Liyaqūlū Darasta Wa Linubayyinahu Liqawmin Ya`lamūna
  6,106,Attabi` Mā 'Ūĥiya 'Ilayka Min Rabbika Lā 'Ilāha 'Illā Huwa Wa 'A`riđ `Ani Al-Mushrikīna
  6,107,Wa Law Shā'a Allāhu Mā 'Ashrakū Wa Mā Ja`alnāka `Alayhim Ĥafīžāan Wa Mā 'Anta `Alayhim Biwakīlin
  6,108,Wa Lā Tasubbū Al-Ladhīna Yad`ūna Min Dūni Allāhi Fayasubbū Allāha `Adwan Bighayri `Ilmin Kadhālika Zayyannā Likulli 'Ummatin `Amalahum Thumma 'Ilá Rabbihim Marji`uhum Fayunabbi'uhum Bimā Kānū Ya`malūna
  6,109,Wa 'Aqsamū Billāhi Jahda 'Aymānihim La'in Jā'at/hum 'Āyatun Layu'uminunna Bihā Qul 'Innamā Al-'Āyātu `Inda Allāhi Wa Mā Yush`irukum 'Annahā 'Idhā Jā'at Lā Yu'uminūna
  6,110,Wa Nuqallibu 'Af'idatahum Wa 'Abşārahum Kamā Lam Yu'uminū Bihi 'Awwala Marratin Wa Nadharuhum Fī Ţughyānihim Ya`mahūna